name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Youtube Searching Embeded in Google Search

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This adds a tab for Youtube search directly on Google search.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Google Videos Search sometimes doesn't give you what you want and sends you to weird sites. This extension adds a Youtube button to direct your search directly to Youtube! It's been very useful for me, especially when I'm looking up Tutorials
